{"type": "article", "id": 19420, "title": "树桩便签纸", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-21T07:40:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134735p8tDOdBWh7qHanml.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这个像树桩一样的便签纸是一个不错的办公室点缀。它一共有 70 页，每一页都是圆形的带年轮的纸，一层一层撕开，年轮的图案不变，有种循环往复的感觉。便签下面带有白色或棕色的树根状的底座，很可爱。可以夹在书里当书签或是贴在墙上，让生活多了一份童趣。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145922Zmg18YnBk6lDV0zs.jpg\" width=\"724\" height=\"361\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.49861878\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145922XincNLbMVWHxehZs.jpg\" width=\"678\" height=\"504\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74336283\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145922ePMlRDfz8Z7aBq15.jpg\" width=\"678\" height=\"470\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69321534\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261459233rZPdRuh90jyEliH.jpg\" width=\"658\" height=\"467\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70972644\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}